                  </hi>. I am a policeman. The prisoner was given into my cus<lb></lb>tody, with the brushes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man laid hold of me, and charged me with stealing the brushes, which I never did.</p>
